data.description: Welcome to your new home at 169 Foy Lockamy in Jacksonville, North Carolina!  I'm excited to introduce you to this wonderful single-story residence that combines comfort, convenience, and an unbeatable location.This charming home features three bedrooms and two full bathrooms, offering the perfect amount of space for your family and guests. With a two-car attached garage, daily living is made effortlessly convenient.Step into the expansive backyard, where you'll discover a spacious oasis complete with a welcoming firepit. Imagine the evenings spent gathered around the warm glow, making memories with loved ones and friends.But the appeal doesn't stop at your front door. The location of this property is simply outstanding. Nestled in Jacksonville, you'll have quick access to the vibrant downtown scene, where a variety of attractions and dining options await your exploration.For those who crave outdoor adventure, you'll find yourself surrounded by parks, hiking trails, and recreational areas that are perfect for staying active and enjoying the natural beauty of the area. And if you're a beach enthusiast, the pristine shores of North Carolina's stunning beaches are just a short drive away.This home at 169 Foy Lockamy is not just a house; it's an opportunity to embrace a comfortable and convenient lifestyle in a sought-after location. Picture yourself here, creating a life full of wonderful memories.
